{"tid":2157458,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"壹傳媒股東會 黎：無礙集團長遠計劃","createTime":"2020-08-15T05:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T05:04:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c98963835d600e86df7e9368f9bbe6a570639c","tid":2157458,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:04:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/5OAX7UZ6MVDNPKTCKPSAMC2OBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2F5OAX7UZ6MVDNPKTCKPSAMC2OBU%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8QoJw9ynFthkhoOYQBA%2BRXM%3D&h=d094d775\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2F5OAX7UZ6MVDNPKTCKPSAMC2OBU%2F&h=124bf773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/5OAX7UZ6MVDNPKTCKPSAMC2OBU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒股東會 黎：無礙集團長遠計劃<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】《蘋果》無懼強權打壓，壹傳媒（282）主席黎智英昨日出席公司股東會，回應公司財政狀況。對於網民倡議用真金白銀入市，黎覺得這固然是一種支持的姿態，但無助公司業績。被問到哪些方式更為有效，他表示：「訂閱囉！」有股東着緊公司需否安排財務融資，黎智英派定心丸，「我哋唔需要做融資，靠我自己㗎咋」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：特朗普：黎智英被捕可怕  美研制裁紅二代 禁港銀行美元交易<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2vVZeoSs41Jd7OAr-Fpzdcc_LsA=/3236x1251/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FQNT5AWO2BDU5P5R7D3ILD5ZLI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2vVZeoSs41Jd7OAr-Fpzdcc_LsA%3D%2F3236x1251%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFQNT5AWO2BDU5P5R7D3ILD5ZLI.jpg&h=3c4d46d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■壹傳媒主席黎智英、行政總裁張劍虹及營運總裁兼財務總裁周達權昨出席股東會，黎向股東派定心丸，指公司毋須安排財務融資。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指訂閱支持好過買股票<br />\n<br />\n黎智英周一被警方拘捕，壹傳媒編採部門亦遭大肆搜查。黎智英強調，今次管理層被捕事件不會影響公司運作，而且公司管理。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有出席股東會的小股東表示，已持有壹傳媒股票逾五年，即使近日股價飆升。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n然而，股價飆升惹起配股融資疑雲。黎智英接受彭博訪問時表明，他排除今。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於證監會調查壹傳媒的股票交易，黎智英在股東會後接受本報查詢時指，證監會自能掌握是誰在買貨，「。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張劍虹：做好《蘋果》感謝市民<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒行政總裁張劍虹在股東會後見記者，指周二晚保釋後，警方未有與他聯。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CKiPyWgVUAeTyWzd0rKUfFw8UJw=/1396x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZLIMSX7HYFDIBCBYJUKO6YNC5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCKiPyWgVUAeTyWzd0rKUfFw8UJw%3D%2F1396x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZLIMSX7HYFDIBCBYJUKO6YNC5E.jpg&h=6b6b6abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■張劍虹於股東會後見傳媒，指《蘋果》廣告收入及網上訂閱人數有明顯增長。"}]}